r for 2nd player)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2102640/extras/21f9a6fa5c54a21db2e74d32454a417a.poster.avif?t=1758144050\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2102640/extras/21f9a6fa5c54a21db2e74d32454a417a.webm?t=1758144050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2102640/extras/21f9a6fa5c54a21db2e74d32454a417a.mp4?t=1758144050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Season Mode:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play in a randomly generated 14 game kickball season</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Look out for angry Mom or Dad who may try to ruin your fun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make it to the playoffs for a chance to win the Kickball Kup!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2102640/extras/aa3a8cc465ba4a685e0ade2bd3e893bf.poster.avif?t=1758144050\" width=598 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2102640/extras/aa3a8cc465ba4a685e0ade2bd3e893bf.webm?t=1758144050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2102640/extras/aa3a8cc465ba4a685e0ade2bd3e893bf.mp4?t=1758144050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
